            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pizzas are ready, top them with <strong>basil leaves</strong></p><p>Drizzle over a little <strong>olive oil</strong> – these are your <strong>margherita pomodoro pizzas</strong></p>",
